data.description: Located in the heart of Awendaw, this cozy 2 bedroom, 1.5 bath cottage is situated on a wooded 1.35 ac site with 93' of frontage on Hwy 17. Great home with roomy front porch, nice size rear screened porch, back yard w/ fire pit. Updates include new roof in 2023, well pump in 2022, fridge & water heater in 2018. Mini Split HVAC. Home is conveniently located with easy access to north Mt. Pleasant and McClellanville. Awendaw Creek is a short walk away as is the Francis Marion forest with miles and miles of trails and natural beauty.
